<p>This page provides constituency-level totals of gambling premises in the UK using <a href="https://www.gamblingcommission.gov.uk/public-register/premises/download">data from the Gambling Commission</a>.</p>
<p>The number of slot machine shops has risen by 7% since 2022 as new "adult gaming centres" have been created. These can be <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2025/may/18/slot-machine-firms-uk-poorest-areas-andy-burnham">disproportionately concentrated in some of Britain's most-deprived areas</a>.</p>

